type: dataset
date-released: 2026-04-01
url: "https://github.com/NickGillArizona/Displacing-Deference-Data-and-Doctrine-for-a-Disability-Centered-AFFH"
repository-code: "https://github.com/NickGillArizona/Displacing-Deference-Data-and-Doctrine-for-a-Disability-Centered-AFFH"
abstract: >-
  Replication package for a law review note arguing that the post-Loper Bright
  constitutional landscape counsels recalibrating AFFH through the disability-specific
  mandates of 42 U.S.C. § 3604(f)(3). Contains the FHA Unified Database (2,522
  screened-in federal FHA cases; 1,720 disability), classification pipeline
  documentation, Census PUMS analysis scripts, and supplementary appendices.
keywords:
  - fair housing act
  - disability
  - AFFH
  - Loper Bright
  - empirical legal studies
  - LLM classification
